  "body": "### Description\n\nThere are many ways to prevent API scraping but an 'easy' way to achieve that is through the obfuscation of ids.\r\n\r\nIn the following list you can find libraries in java/ruby that do that.\r\n\r\n**Java**\r\n1. https://github.com/sqids/sqids-java\r\n2. https://github.com/jchambers/id-obfuscator\r\n\r\n**Ruby**\r\n1. https://github.com/bullet-train-co/bullet_train-core/tree/main/bullet_train-obfuscates_id\r\n2. https://github.com/wbotelhos/idy\r\n3. https://github.com/danidemi/obfuscated-ids\r\n\r\nFor example if this feature is enabled in a Quarkus application it would convert automatically the `@PathParam` from the obfuscated id to the real id.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
